      <title>Atos 达成重组协议，债权人获得控制权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/french-it-firm-atos-reaches-restructuring-deal-with-creditors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Atos SE 的债权人与该公司达成协议，他们将而不是外部投资者来控制这家陷入困境的法国 IT 服务公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/french-it-firm-atos-reaches-restructuring-deal-with-creditors</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 16:20:49 GMT</pubDate>
